* Time Zone\nSelection
** DST Impact
***_ Hourly jobs may skip or delay
***_ Spring forward: skip a run
***_ Fall back: run twice
** Use UTC When
***_ Exact intervals required
***_ UTC timestamp data sources
***_ Cross-region coordination
** Use Local Time When
***_ Business alignment needed
***_ 8 AM local delivery expected
***_ DST shifts acceptable
@endmindmap
